706517f-a.text:
1380-1384 Rockaway P'kway., at the S.W. corner of Smith's Lane. Originally known as Harm's Hall. A view of the Democratic Club of Canarsie in 1929; Subsecuently (1933) it was occupied by the Holy Family Athletic Club. (Catholic).
July 6, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
